### Create a Todo
POST http://localhost:5000/api/todos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Complete project documentation",
  "description": "Write comprehensive docs for new feature"
}

### Response saved as {{todoId}}

### List Todos
GET http://localhost:5000/api/todos?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Single Todo
GET http://localhost:5000/api/todos/{{todoId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Todo (Mark as Complete)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/todos/{{todoId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Complete project documentation",
  "description": "Write comprehensive docs for new feature",
  "completed": true
}

### Delete Todo
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/todos/{{todoId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Non-Existent Todo (Should return 404)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/todos/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create Todo with Missing Title (Should return 400)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/todos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "description": "Missing title field"
}

### Create Todo with Very Long Title (Validation test)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/todos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "This is an extremely long title that exceeds the maximum allowed length for a todo item to test validation and ensure the API properly rejects invalid input according to business rules and requirements",
  "description": "Test long title validation"
}

### List Todos with Pagination
GET http://localhost:5000/api/todos?page=2&pageSize=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List Todos without Auth (Should return 401)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/todos

### Create Todo with Invalid JSON (Should return 400)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/todos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Valid title",
  "invalid json here"
}

### Filter Todos by Status
GET http://localhost:5000/api/todos?completed=false
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Search Todos by Title
GET http://localhost:5000/api/todos/search?query=project
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Todos Count
GET http://localhost:5000/api/todos/count
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Bulk Delete Todos
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/todos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "ids": ["{{todoId}}", "{{todoId2}}"]
}
